name: Scorched Cell
category: Effects
footprint: 1x1
facing: no
shadow: no
blocks_light: no
height: 0.01
placement: floor
room_types: boss-chamber, battlefield-recent, forge, refinery, demiplane-laboratory, elemental-fire-node, dark-temple
typical_count: many
clusters_with: scorch-mark, ash-pile, bloodstain, bone-pile, rubble, corpse
notes: Burned blackened floor decal covering most of a cell — large fire or blast damage with ash scatter. Tileable for wide damage areas.
---
# Flat floor decal

# === Outer char haze (fills most of cell — faded perimeter) ===
rect 0.02,0.02 0.96,0.96 fill #2a1810 0.35

# === Main burn blob (large irregular shape covering most of cell) ===
poly 0.08,0.34 0.12,0.18 0.24,0.08 0.42,0.04 0.58,0.04 0.76,0.10 0.88,0.22 0.94,0.38 0.96,0.54 0.90,0.72 0.78,0.86 0.60,0.94 0.42,0.96 0.24,0.92 0.12,0.80 0.06,0.62 fill #1a0a04 0.9
